create contexts/TodoContext.js
    - import createContext, useContext
    - export TodoContext, useTodo, TodoProvider
    - creating array & methods in TodoContext

create contexts/index.js
    - exporting all the neccessities from TodoContext

App.jsx
    - create state for todos
    - include TodoProvider
    - define addTodo()
    - define updateTodo()
    - define deleteTodo()
    - define toggleCOmplete()
    - useEffect() to load all the tasks form the local storage
    - useEffect() to add the new task to the local storage

create components/index.js
    - import & export TodoForm, TodoItem

create components/TodoForm.jsx
    - create a form to add task
    - create state for a todo
    - access addTodo() using useTodo hook
    - create add() to add a new task
    - add 'value' and 'onChange()' properties to 'input'

create components/TodoItem.jsx
    - create a 'div' to display the todo items
    - access updateTodo(), deleteTodo(), toggleComplete() from useTodo hook
    - create state for isTodoEditable, todoMsg
    - define editTodo() to update a todo
    - define toggleCompleted() to toggle the task complete status

App.jsx
    - add the TodoForm
    - add the TodoItem, pass prop for 'todo'

